Use the standard library
This is how to sum_to_n of n:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Increase i
      Remember that total is sum of total and i
   End do
   The answer is total
Now you know

>>> sum_to_n of 30
465
>>> sum_to_n of 100
5050
>>> sum_to_n of 5
15